headline.main: 4 LIVE FOR 6 WEEKS ON ASTRONAUT DIET

results.snippet: DAYTON, Ohio, Nov. 26 (AP) -- Four college men who lived on astronaut food for six weeks sat down to Thanksgiving dinner today, apparently none the worse for wear and richer by $1,000 each. They were also cleaner than they had been in 42 days.
